quran[5{c,v,t}:
39,6,isi ne tum ko 1 shakhs se pedakiya phir is se is ka jora banaya aur isi ne tumahray liye chaar payon mein se aath jore banaye. wohi tum ko tumhari maaon ke pait mein ( pehlay ) aik terhan phir doosri terhan teen andheron mein banata hai. yahi khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai isi ki badshahi hai. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi phir tum kahan phiray jatay ho ?
39,7,agar nashukri karo ge to khuda tum se be parwa hai. aur woh apne bundon ke liye nashukri pasand nahi karta aur agar shukar karo ge to woh is ko tumahray liye pasand kere ga. aur koi uthany wala dosray ka boojh nahi uthaye ga. phir tum apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lootna hai. phir jo kuch tum karte rahay woh tum ko betaye ga. woh to dilon ki posheeda baton taq se aagah hai
39,8,aur jab ensaan ko takleef pahunchti hai to apne perwar-digaar ko pukaarta ( aur ) is ki taraf dil se rujoo karta hai. phir jab woh is ko apni taraf se koi Nemat deta hai to jis kaam ke liye pehlay is ko pukaarta hai usay bhool jata hai aur khuda ka shareek bananay lagta hai taakay ( logon ko ) is ke raste se gumraah kere. keh do ke ( ae kafir Nemat ) apni nashukri se thora sa faida uthalay. phir too to dozakhiyon mein hoga
39,9,( bhala mushriq acha hai ) ya woh jo raat ke waqton mein zameen par peshani rakh kar aur kharray ho kar ibadat karta aur akhirat se darta aur apne perwar-digaar ki rehmat ki umeed rakhta hai. kaho bhala jo log ilm rakhtay hain aur jo nahi rakhtay dono barabar ho saktay hain? ( aur ) nasiyaat to wohi pakarte hain jo aqalmand hain
39,10,keh do ke ae mere Bandoo jo imaan laaye ho apne perwar-digaar se daro. jinhon ne is duniya mein neki ki un ke liye bhalai hai. aur khuda ki zameen kushadah hai. jo sabr karne walay hain un ko be shumaar sawab miley ga
